# Repo-wide ShellCheck config. Disables info-level findings that the project's established,
# deliberate patterns trigger, so `scripts/dev/lint-scripts` stays green across all scripts
# (existing and new) without editing each one:
#
#   SC1091  Sourced `common`/libs are located at runtime via a computed path; ShellCheck
#           cannot follow the dynamic path. Those files are linted separately as their own
#           inputs, so following is unnecessary.
#   SC2015  The `A && B || C` shorthand (e.g. `... || true` guards) is used intentionally.
#   SC2016  Single-quoted regex / ACL patterns (e.g. in scripts/doctor) must NOT expand.
#
# Warnings and errors are still reported.
disable=SC1091,SC2015,SC2016
